PROFESSIONAL BIOGRAPHY
Products And/Or Services :
Provides a complete set of interactive, internet based decision-making tools and databases which support all commercial ship chartering activities. Formed in June 2000 and has over 450 clients for its 4 specialized product lines: AXS Dry, Alphaliner, AXSS & P, and AXS Tanker. The products and solutions are purposely built for ship brokers, operators, owners, characters, research firms and financial institutions, using state of the art internet technologies
 
Affiliations Awards :
British Chamber of Commerce in Singapore
 
More About me :
Stephen is the Commercial Director for AXS Marine, a company producing a comprehensive set of interactive database and decision making tools for all types of clients in the marine industry. Launching his career as a Logistics Coordinator for both Global Equipment Management and EacBen Container Services Ltd., Stephen continued to build an impressive two and a half decades of industry experience, advancing through marketing, terminal, equipment, commercial sales and directorship positions. Joining AXS Marine in 2006, Stephen has been responsible for business sales and product growth on a global scale, drawing on his extensive international experience to manage European and Asian sales teams, all while spearheading the company’s marketing initiatives and service delivery teams. 





